1
00:00:52,280 --> 00:00:53,160
Look everyone,

2
00:00:53,320 --> 00:00:55,680
this is the archaeological excavation site.

3
00:00:55,680 --> 00:00:57,410
Right now, it's being cleaned.

4
00:01:05,440 --> 00:01:06,240
What's wrong?

5
00:01:06,440 --> 00:01:07,360
Why so down?

6
00:01:07,800 --> 00:01:09,360
Some people are causing trouble outside,

7
00:01:09,360 --> 00:01:11,200
and it's affecting your state of mind.

8
00:01:11,200 --> 00:01:14,060
You are too easily distracted by the outside world.

9
00:01:14,520 --> 00:01:15,440
A peaceful mind

10
00:01:16,200 --> 00:01:19,360
is a fundamental quality

11
00:01:20,200 --> 00:01:21,660
for an artifact restorer.

12
00:01:21,840 --> 00:01:22,500
Professor,

13
00:01:22,720 --> 00:01:24,560
what about our smashed assignments?

14
00:01:24,560 --> 00:01:25,560
Don't worry about that.

15
00:01:25,560 --> 00:01:26,760
As for your assignments,

16
00:01:26,760 --> 00:01:29,400
I have already evaluated and graded them.

17
00:01:29,440 --> 00:01:30,920
I even took photos of them.

18
00:01:31,120 --> 00:01:33,320
Even though the porcelain pieces

19
00:01:33,320 --> 00:01:34,800
for Xu Xiao and Yan Xue's groups

20
00:01:34,800 --> 00:01:35,729
were destroyed.

21
00:01:36,240 --> 00:01:37,320
But it doesn't matter.

22
00:01:37,320 --> 00:01:38,479
Your grades are recorded,

23
00:01:38,479 --> 00:01:39,740
and we have the photos.

24
00:01:39,920 --> 00:01:40,920
After class,

25
00:01:41,000 --> 00:01:42,729
you can feel free to check them.

26
00:01:47,560 --> 00:01:48,200
Class.

27
00:01:48,600 --> 00:01:49,800
Whether it's history

28
00:01:50,560 --> 00:01:52,280
or a small fragment of life,

29
00:01:52,560 --> 00:01:54,720
it will leave a trace as long as it happens.

30
00:01:54,720 --> 00:01:57,240
No matter how thick the dirt on it is,

31
00:01:57,320 --> 00:01:58,979
there will eventually be a day

32
00:01:59,280 --> 00:02:00,560
when it regains its glory

33
00:02:00,560 --> 00:02:02,290
and sees the light of day again.

34
00:02:03,640 --> 00:02:04,240
All right,

35
00:02:04,640 --> 00:02:06,100
let's continue the class.

36
00:02:07,840 --> 00:02:08,320
Come,

37
00:02:08,560 --> 00:02:10,199
everyone look at this photo.

38
00:02:10,919 --> 00:02:15,850
These are the characteristics of ceramics from the Chenghua period of the Ming Dynasty.

39
00:02:23,160 --> 00:02:24,079
Mr. Yue.

40
00:02:25,960 --> 00:02:27,090
What is it, Xiaocen?

41
00:02:28,560 --> 00:02:29,360
If

42
00:02:29,960 --> 00:02:30,760
there are no broken porcelain pieces

43
00:02:30,760 --> 00:02:32,760
for us to complete the restoration,

44
00:02:33,160 --> 00:02:34,240
I want to ask,

45
00:02:34,600 --> 00:02:36,120
is there any other way

46
00:02:36,120 --> 00:02:37,780
to prove Xu Xiao's innocence?

47
00:02:39,079 --> 00:02:39,840
At that time,

48
00:02:40,160 --> 00:02:42,000
were there no broken pieces left at the scene

49
00:02:42,000 --> 00:02:43,320
at all?

50
00:02:44,640 --> 00:02:45,880
I specifically checked.

51
00:02:45,880 --> 00:02:46,810
There were none.

52
00:02:49,320 --> 00:02:51,000
This is a bit difficult.

53
00:02:52,200 --> 00:02:52,800
By the way,

54
00:02:54,000 --> 00:02:55,840
are there any photos or anything?

55
00:02:55,840 --> 00:02:57,200
They could help corroborate

56
00:02:57,200 --> 00:02:58,480
the shape of that cup

57
00:02:58,560 --> 00:02:59,760
or its patterns.

58
00:03:01,640 --> 00:03:02,160
Right.

59
00:03:02,800 --> 00:03:04,800
The antique shop has surveillance.

60
00:03:05,200 --> 00:03:06,260
Thank you, Mr. Yue.

61
00:03:06,680 --> 00:03:07,680
Goodbye, Mr. Yue.

62
00:03:09,080 --> 00:03:09,720
Boss.

63
00:03:10,680 --> 00:03:11,480
Boss.

64
00:03:13,120 --> 00:03:13,680
Boss.

65
00:03:16,600 --> 00:03:17,000
Xiaocen.

66
00:03:17,000 --> 00:03:17,520
Boss.

67
00:03:17,800 --> 00:03:21,329
Could you help me check the surveillance footage from that day?

68
00:03:23,640 --> 00:03:25,100
It's about Xu Xiao, right?

69
00:03:25,520 --> 00:03:25,960
Yes.

70
00:03:26,840 --> 00:03:28,500
I heard about the livestream.

71
00:03:30,600 --> 00:03:32,160
I knew you'd come for the footage.

72
00:03:32,160 --> 00:03:33,079
I have it ready for you.

73
00:03:33,079 --> 00:03:34,340
Right here on my phone.

74
00:03:34,880 --> 00:03:36,560
These people went too far.

75
00:03:37,760 --> 00:03:39,000
If they want to inspect the bowls, let them.

76
00:03:39,000 --> 00:03:40,640
Why drag Xu Xiao's father into this?

77
00:03:40,640 --> 00:03:42,960
This is an issue between two different generations.

78
00:03:42,960 --> 00:03:45,480
Boss, you know about Xu Xiao's father?

79
00:03:49,600 --> 00:03:51,480
You wouldn't know since you're not from around here.

80
00:03:51,480 --> 00:03:53,600
But it was a big deal back then.

81
00:03:54,000 --> 00:03:55,160
As for Xu Xiao,

82
00:03:55,440 --> 00:03:57,000
he made such a big mistake.

83
00:03:57,440 --> 00:03:59,370
So why did the school cover for him?

84
00:03:59,760 --> 00:04:00,690
I looked into it.

85
00:04:01,080 --> 00:04:01,740
It turns out

86
00:04:02,120 --> 00:04:03,880
his teacher, Yue Qixin,

87
00:04:04,320 --> 00:04:05,240
and his father,

88
00:04:05,400 --> 00:04:06,480
Xu Jinsong,

89
00:04:06,960 --> 00:04:07,800
these two

90
00:04:08,360 --> 00:04:10,480
were fellow disciples.

91
00:04:11,080 --> 00:04:13,680
Xu Jinsong was caught selling fakes back then.

92
00:04:13,720 --> 00:04:14,840
He couldn't handle the shock

93
00:04:14,840 --> 00:04:15,920
and lost his mind.

94
00:04:16,519 --> 00:04:18,320
Later, on that ceramics street,

95
00:04:18,560 --> 00:04:20,320
he would argue with people every day holding fakes,

96
00:04:20,320 --> 00:04:21,779
insisting they were real.

97
00:04:22,120 --> 00:04:23,800
Do you think this is karma?

98
00:04:26,120 --> 00:04:27,160
These arguments,

99
00:04:27,160 --> 00:04:27,800
you don't need to tell me.

100
00:04:27,800 --> 00:04:28,440
I know it all, okay?

101
00:04:28,440 --> 00:04:29,240
No, Mr. Xu.

102
00:04:29,240 --> 00:04:30,080
I still say the same thing.

103
00:04:30,080 --> 00:04:31,920
When it comes to judging at a glance,

104
00:04:31,920 --> 00:04:33,980
I, Xu Jinsong, have never been wrong.

105
00:04:42,240 --> 00:04:43,320
How is it faded?

106
00:04:46,000 --> 00:04:48,240
I think Yue Qixin is just jealous.

107
00:04:51,720 --> 00:04:52,800
I, Xu Jinsong,

108
00:04:52,800 --> 00:04:54,120
have never been wrong.

109
00:04:55,960 --> 00:04:57,220
I heard you sell fakes.

110
00:04:57,240 --> 00:04:58,560
My item must be a fake too.

111
00:04:58,560 --> 00:04:59,000
Give me a refund.

112
00:04:59,000 --> 00:04:59,640
Alright, alright, alright.

113
00:04:59,640 --> 00:05:01,480
I, Xu Jinsong, have never sold fake goods.

114
00:05:01,480 --> 00:05:02,680
Then how can you prove it's not fake?

115
00:05:02,680 --> 00:05:03,720
What do you mean, how can I prove it?

116
00:05:03,720 --> 00:05:05,520
I'm telling you, I've never sold fake goods.

117
00:05:05,520 --> 00:05:06,450
Give me a refund.

118
00:05:21,360 --> 00:05:22,000
Mr. Yue.

119
00:05:23,120 --> 00:05:24,180
The shape is right.

120
00:05:25,280 --> 00:05:27,960
But the resolution of this surveillance footage is too poor.

121
00:05:27,960 --> 00:05:29,290
I can't see the pattern.

122
00:05:29,480 --> 00:05:30,200
Mr. Yue.

123
00:05:30,760 --> 00:05:31,880
What should we do?

124
00:05:32,880 --> 00:05:33,480
Mr. Yue.

125
00:05:37,560 --> 00:05:38,840
What is it, Xu Xiao?

126
00:05:47,680 --> 00:05:49,810
I want to take some time off from school

127
00:05:49,880 --> 00:05:51,280
to deal with this properly.

128
00:05:51,280 --> 00:05:52,680
Don't let this matter

129
00:05:52,680 --> 00:05:53,800
ruin your future.

130
00:05:54,159 --> 00:05:55,360
Your studies should come first.

131
00:05:55,360 --> 00:05:55,920
Xu Xiao,

132
00:05:56,520 --> 00:05:57,600
there must be a way.

133
00:05:58,400 --> 00:06:01,120
We have a centralized garbage station in Jingdezhen.

134
00:06:01,120 --> 00:06:02,240
If archaeologists

135
00:06:02,240 --> 00:06:05,100
can unearth tens of thousands of porcelain shards,

136
00:06:05,760 --> 00:06:06,560
then I can definitely find

137
00:06:06,560 --> 00:06:08,600
the shards of that blue and white porcelain bowl.

138
00:06:08,600 --> 00:06:09,480
Xiaocen,

139
00:06:10,240 --> 00:06:12,770
that's not what I meant by persistence, okay?

140
00:06:12,880 --> 00:06:14,410
Do you know how much garbage

141
00:06:14,480 --> 00:06:16,960
a city produces in a single day?

142
00:06:18,000 --> 00:06:18,600
Nonsense.

143
00:06:20,520 --> 00:06:21,720
I'll solve it myself.

144
00:06:21,760 --> 00:06:22,240
Xu Xiao,

145
00:06:22,680 --> 00:06:23,640
about this matter,

146
00:06:23,640 --> 00:06:25,760
I suggest you think it over carefully.

147
00:06:25,760 --> 00:06:26,490
Understood?

148
00:06:38,440 --> 00:06:39,000
Xu Xiao.

149
00:06:41,120 --> 00:06:41,800
Xu Xiao.

150
00:06:43,440 --> 00:06:44,000
Xu Xiao.

151
00:06:45,960 --> 00:06:48,290
We're all still trying to find a solution.

152
00:06:48,800 --> 00:06:50,659
Making this kind of decision now,

153
00:06:51,200 --> 00:06:51,920
will suspending your studies solve anything?

154
00:06:51,920 --> 00:06:54,120
I told you I have my own way to solve this.

155
00:06:55,280 --> 00:06:58,340
How could I really let you go digging through the trash?

156
00:07:22,280 --> 00:07:22,720
Mom.

157
00:07:24,680 --> 00:07:26,540
About what you mentioned before,

158
00:07:27,360 --> 00:07:28,760
I've thought it through.

159
00:07:33,600 --> 00:07:34,320
Today,

160
00:07:36,080 --> 00:07:38,540
I applied for a leave of absence from school.

161
00:07:40,480 --> 00:07:41,080
Really?

162
00:07:43,000 --> 00:07:44,240
That's great, son.

163
00:07:45,760 --> 00:07:46,960
I'll have your uncle

164
00:07:46,960 --> 00:07:48,690
find the best tutor right away.

165
00:07:49,560 --> 00:07:51,920
Don't worry. Your grades have always been good.

166
00:07:51,920 --> 00:07:52,640
Anyway,

167
00:07:52,680 --> 00:07:54,480
no matter what major you choose,

168
00:07:54,640 --> 00:07:56,500
you won't fall behind your peers.

169
00:07:58,600 --> 00:07:59,200
Got it.

170
00:08:00,840 --> 00:08:04,440
The most important thing when choosing a major is to be cautious.

171
00:08:04,480 --> 00:08:05,880
Mom will help you choose.

172
00:08:07,760 --> 00:08:09,360
Well, Xu Xiao.

173
00:08:11,560 --> 00:08:13,690
Have you really thought this through?

174
00:08:14,600 --> 00:08:15,960
What are you talking about?

175
00:08:15,960 --> 00:08:18,080
Didn't I tell you to find a tutor?

176
00:08:18,320 --> 00:08:19,080
Right.

177
00:08:19,800 --> 00:08:21,130
I'll go contact one now.

178
00:08:23,320 --> 00:08:23,920
Son,

179
00:08:24,560 --> 00:08:27,420
I am really happy that you are willing to listen to me

180
00:08:27,920 --> 00:08:29,360
on this matter this time.

181
00:08:33,960 --> 00:08:36,400
We've talked about cleaning before.

182
00:08:36,520 --> 00:08:38,720
For cleaning, we need to do a rough wash.

183
00:08:38,840 --> 00:08:40,799
And we also need professional cleaning agents

184
00:08:40,799 --> 00:08:42,520
for precise wiping.

185
00:08:42,799 --> 00:08:43,880
After that,

186
00:08:43,960 --> 00:08:46,600
we'll move on to the next step, splicing.

187
00:08:47,320 --> 00:08:48,960
For splicing, please note

188
00:08:49,440 --> 00:08:51,570
that it must be aligned with the notch.

189
00:10:02,320 --> 00:10:03,050
Look at mine.

190
00:10:04,560 --> 00:10:06,890
I heard Xu Xiao is changing his major soon.

191
00:10:08,120 --> 00:10:09,680
The school isn't pursuing the matter anymore.

192
00:10:09,680 --> 00:10:10,760
Why is he dropping out then?

193
00:10:10,760 --> 00:10:11,200
Exactly.

194
00:10:11,200 --> 00:10:12,720
It seems he brought it up himself.

195
00:10:12,720 --> 00:10:13,800
That shouldn't be the case.

196
00:10:13,800 --> 00:10:15,320
Mr. Yue even spoke up for him.

197
00:10:15,320 --> 00:10:16,600
Don't spread false rumors.

198
00:10:16,600 --> 00:10:17,040
Exactly.

199
00:10:17,040 --> 00:10:18,520
When I was walking from the office just now,

200
00:10:18,520 --> 00:10:19,200
I heard it.

201
00:10:20,600 --> 00:10:22,440
Zhang Jiatian is already causing trouble at school.

202
00:10:22,440 --> 00:10:22,880
Exactly.

203
00:10:22,880 --> 00:10:24,520
Now he has even more reason to make an issue out of it.

204
00:10:24,520 --> 00:10:26,280
What's that idiom again?

205
00:10:26,360 --> 00:10:27,640
Confessing without being pressed.

206
00:10:27,640 --> 00:10:29,040
That's not how you use it.

207
00:10:29,200 --> 00:10:29,560
No.

208
00:10:29,920 --> 00:10:32,320
I don't think Xu Xiao will give up so easily.

209
00:10:33,360 --> 00:10:34,440
Alright, students.

210
00:10:34,440 --> 00:10:35,570
The teacher is here.

211
00:10:35,920 --> 00:10:36,850
Take your seats.

212
00:10:37,240 --> 00:10:38,040
Class begins.

213
00:10:45,200 --> 00:10:45,840
Use this glue.

214
00:10:45,840 --> 00:10:47,640
You have to do it like this. Look.

215
00:10:49,440 --> 00:10:52,600
I didn't expect Mr. Yue to put us in the same group.

216
00:10:53,600 --> 00:10:55,040
Let me make this clear first.

217
00:10:55,040 --> 00:10:57,160
Even though I'm good friends with Yuexin,

218
00:10:57,160 --> 00:10:59,240
I believe in the freedom to love.

219
00:10:59,480 --> 00:11:01,560
So whoever you end up with,

220
00:11:01,560 --> 00:11:01,960
No.

221
00:11:01,960 --> 00:11:03,440
I will give you my blessing. No, wait.

222
00:11:03,440 --> 00:11:05,960
Besides, I'm quite clumsy.

223
00:11:06,280 --> 00:11:08,920
Don't expect too much from me.

224
00:11:09,360 --> 00:11:09,760
Please

225
00:11:10,720 --> 00:11:11,920
bear with me.

226
00:11:20,440 --> 00:11:20,960
Cen.

227
00:11:22,520 --> 00:11:23,980
Where are you going later?

228
00:11:30,840 --> 00:11:31,840
This is so cute.

229
00:11:37,400 --> 00:11:37,800
Cen.

230
00:11:39,280 --> 00:11:42,410
Isn't that the person who took advantage of us last time?

231
00:11:45,040 --> 00:11:46,480
Yes, that's her.

232
00:11:51,400 --> 00:11:52,260
She's leaving.

233
00:11:52,440 --> 00:11:54,170
Let's go take advantage of her.

234
00:12:05,600 --> 00:12:07,720
Great. Great.

235
00:12:10,040 --> 00:12:11,480
So cute. Look.

236
00:12:12,120 --> 00:12:12,560
For you.

237
00:12:12,560 --> 00:12:13,680
So cute.

238
00:12:13,720 --> 00:12:14,920
Thank you, Yuexin.

239
00:12:22,160 --> 00:12:22,800
Xiao Cen.

240
00:12:23,640 --> 00:12:26,040
Do you know how I noticed Xu Xiao?

241
00:12:31,800 --> 00:12:33,720
Your girls' group failed the military posture.

242
00:12:33,720 --> 00:12:35,240
What's wrong with me punishing her?

243
00:12:35,240 --> 00:12:36,480
Why are you talking back to me?

244
00:12:36,480 --> 00:12:38,010
Wu Jing has tried very hard.

245
00:12:38,280 --> 00:12:39,800
If you let her keep standing like this,

246
00:12:39,800 --> 00:12:41,200
she will get heatstroke.

247
00:12:41,240 --> 00:12:42,880
I don't think I said anything wrong.

248
00:12:42,880 --> 00:12:43,480
Fine then.

249
00:12:43,800 --> 00:12:45,600
You take the punishment for her.

250
00:12:50,120 --> 00:12:50,980
I'm Lin Yuexin.

251
00:12:54,360 --> 00:12:55,000
Xu Xiao.

252
00:12:57,240 --> 00:12:59,320
When the instructor scolded us just now,

253
00:12:59,320 --> 00:13:00,520
you didn't say a word.

254
00:13:01,280 --> 00:13:02,680
So why were you punished?

255
00:13:03,040 --> 00:13:04,240
Because in our group,

256
00:13:04,280 --> 00:13:05,920
some boys didn't do their chores well.

257
00:13:05,920 --> 00:13:06,800
Then why

258
00:13:07,120 --> 00:13:08,780
are you the only one punished?

259
00:13:09,200 --> 00:13:09,720
And him.

260
00:13:09,720 --> 00:13:10,600
Seventh lap.

261
00:13:11,120 --> 00:13:12,240
Eight laps left.

262
00:13:13,400 --> 00:13:14,730
I can't do this anymore.

263
00:13:15,920 --> 00:13:17,600
Why did they choose you as the group leader?

264
00:13:17,600 --> 00:13:18,730
I don't know either.

265
00:13:19,440 --> 00:13:21,560
It seems that since the first grade,

266
00:13:21,960 --> 00:13:24,160
I've been the class monitor every year.

267
00:13:25,720 --> 00:13:28,380
Then why did they choose you as the group leader?

268
00:13:28,600 --> 00:13:30,660
Because I'm the tallest in our class.

269
00:13:35,280 --> 00:13:37,040
I guess it was around that time

270
00:13:37,680 --> 00:13:39,800
that I became curious about this boy.

271
00:13:41,040 --> 00:13:42,040
His excellence

272
00:13:42,360 --> 00:13:44,120
and inexplicable persistence

273
00:13:45,760 --> 00:13:47,360
are very attractive, right?

274
00:13:48,800 --> 00:13:50,000
But

275
00:13:50,480 --> 00:13:51,560
as time went by,

276
00:13:52,040 --> 00:13:53,320
I felt this kind of

277
00:13:53,560 --> 00:13:54,320
care

278
00:13:54,560 --> 00:13:55,480
and concern

279
00:13:56,800 --> 00:13:58,360
was more of an admiration.

280
00:14:00,560 --> 00:14:01,680
Actually...

281
00:14:03,480 --> 00:14:05,800
Last time I volunteered to team up

282
00:14:07,240 --> 00:14:08,440
because of myself.

283
00:14:08,440 --> 00:14:09,120
Xiaocen,

284
00:14:09,560 --> 00:14:11,800
you don't need to explain anything to me.

285
00:14:11,800 --> 00:14:13,440
Just do what you want to do.

286
00:14:17,360 --> 00:14:18,760
Yuexin, you're so sweet.

287
